The,NYC,Subway,Data,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,subway,information,from,New,York,City,s,Metropolitan,Transit,Authority,MTA,and,integrate,it,into,their,own,applications,The,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,subway,station,codes,a,station,s,name,and,coordinates,all,subway,arrival,times,for,a,given,station,and,all,stations,where,a,train,is,stopping,at,a,given,time